These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: fanta, juice, milk, soy-milk
Pet: hedgehog, fish, lizard, chinchilla
1. Pet:chinchilla is on the left of Beverage:milk##1
2. Beverage:fanta is on the left of Pet:fish##1
3. Beverage:soy-milk is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:lizard is on the left or right of Pet:chinchilla##3
5. Beverage:fanta is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta | juice | soy-milk | milk |
| Pet        | hedgehog | fish   | chinchilla | lizard    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: satire, fantasy, family, documentary
Nationality: indian, turkish, spanish, italian
1. Movie-Genre:fantasy is on the left of Movie-Genre:documentary##1
2. Nationality:indian is on the left of Nationality:spanish##1
3. Nationality:spanish is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:indian == Movie-Genre:satire##1
5. Nationality:turkish is on the right of Nationality:spanish##1
6. Nationality:indian == Movie-Genre:satire##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | satire  | fantasy  | documentary |
| Nationality   | italian    | indian | spanish | turkish    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: avocado, peach, tomato, zucchini
Movie-Genre: sports, martial-arts, fantasy, horror
1. Food:zucchini is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:horror##3
2. Food:tomato is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:horror is on the left or right of Food:peach##3
4. Movie-Genre:horror is on the right of Movie-Genre:fantasy##1
5. Movie-Genre:sports is in an odd position##4
6. Food:peach is on the right of Food:tomato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | zucchini | tomato | peach    | avocado      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy        | horror     | sports | martial-arts |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: chess, video-games, fishing, dancing
Music-Genre: jazz, salsa, soul, d&b
1. Hobby:video-games is between Music-Genre:jazz and Music-Genre:d&b##2
2. Hobby:dancing is on the left of Hobby:chess##1
3. Music-Genre:soul is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:salsa is on the left of Music-Genre:d&b##1
5. Music-Genre:salsa is on the right of Hobby:chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | dancing | chess | video-games | fishing |
| Music-Genre   | soul       | jazz   | salsa    | d&b  |

