.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Music-Genre: disco, ambient, indie, blues
Nationality: indonesian, egyptian, turkish, canadian
1. Music-Genre:indie is on the right of Nationality:canadian##1
2. Nationality:egyptian == Music-Genre:blues##1
3. Nationality:turkish is on the right of Music-Genre:disco##1
4. Music-Genre:ambient is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:indie is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:indonesian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | disco    | indie   | blues       |
| Nationality   | indonesian | canadian | turkish | egyptian |

