.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
Movie-Genre: disaster, crime, musical, thriller
Transport: bike, scooter, subway, airplane
1. Transport:airplane is in an odd position##4
2. Transport:subway is on the left of Transport:bike##1
3. Movie-Genre:thriller is on the left of Movie-Genre:musical##1
4. Transport:airplane == Movie-Genre:disaster##1
5. Movie-Genre:thriller is on the left or right of Transport:bike##3
6. Transport:scooter is on the right of Transport:bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | thriller | musical | crime    |
| Transport     | airplane | subway  | bike     | scooter |

