4. Job:photographer is on the right of Pet:chinchilla##1
5. Job:lawyer is between Job:photographer and Job:police-officer##2
6. Pet:hamster is in an odd position##4
7. Pet:hamster is between Job:lawyer and Pet:horse##2
8. Job:lawyer is on the left or right of Job:police-officer##3

