2. Food:radish is on the right of Food:cranberry##1
3. Pet:lizard is between Pet:guinea-pig and Food:grapefruit##2
4. Pet:lizard is in an odd position##4
5. Food:grapefruit == Pet:fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
