.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
Beverage: milk, hot-chocolate, fanta, mirinda
Music-Genre: pop, hip-hop, punk, r&b
1. Beverage:milk == Music-Genre:r&b##1
2. Music-Genre:pop is on the right of Beverage:milk##1
3. Music-Genre:r&b is between Music-Genre:pop and Beverage:fanta##2
4. Beverage:milk is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:r&b is on the left or right of Music-Genre:pop##3
6. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Music-Genre:hip-hop##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate       | fanta   | milk | mirinda |
| Music-Genre   | punk | hip-hop | r&b        | pop    |

